Devin Ratray https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Devin_Ratray 0 Devin D. Ratray (born January 11, 1977) is an American actor, singer and songwriter.He is most famous for his role as Buzz McCallister in Home Alone and Home Alone 2: Lost in New York, but has achieved more recent fame in such films as Nebraska and Blue Ruin.
